{
  "stem": "979.2",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I shiver, you know, when I used to see the Nazis passing-- like little devils in person-- to see such cruelty-- I never saw it to be-- I-- I never could believe it existed.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There he comes in, and he says-- he say to the conductor that-- to the lady-- she was supposed to be our conductor now.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She said that we are going to go to the lager B, which is the one-- the other lager-- that we are going to-- they took a barrack, a big barrack.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they had two-- they had two big rooms, tremendous rooms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in one of the rooms-- it was like two little side rooms for supposedly for the conductor and the block leader.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the other one, the barrack where the girls were going to be, they had bunk beds for a change, you know, like something better than what we saw-- bunk beds like one on top of the other but not together.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and they had like a little sort of a kitchenette on the side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's-- and that's where-- that's where we're gonna sleep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That they say-- they said that from now on, after the two weeks, that we were going to move to this barrack.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were gonna to have an orchestra.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And every time there will be a new person coming, they will-- they will have an-- you know-- when new musician, they will have them slowly, slowly.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The orchestra became 47 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we couldn't believe that this is happening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, it's like-- now I have to go a bit backwards-- something very interesting that I didn't tell you about my father.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My father was a very religious man-- very.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He loved God with all his heart.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
